avatar_container"><div style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog-gold.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/myuradha">myuradha</a></span><span title="2024-02-24 08:00:50" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/9431190">1 year ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"><span class="upvotes">(+1)</span></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>Do you have a guide for using these assets on tiled?</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div id="post-9143191" data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:9143191,&quot;user_id&quot;:3233777}" class="community_post has_vote_column deleted is_deleted has_replies disabled"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><div class="avatar_container"><div style="background-image: url(https://static.itch.io/images/frog-sad.svg)" class="post_avatar"></div></div><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><strong class="name_placeholder">Deleted post</strong></span><span title="2024-01-04 02:27:22" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/9143191">1 year ago</a></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body"><em class="deleted_message">Deleted <span class="2025-03-06 08:45:38">119 days ago</span></em></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies top_level_replies"><div id="post-9143243" data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:9143243,&quot;user_id&quot;:1278838}" class="community_post has_vote_column is_reply"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a href="https://itch.io/profile/seliel-the-shaper" class="avatar_container"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzIwMjE2NzM2LnBuZw==/25x25%23/%2BOhmGY.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/seliel-the-shaper">Seliel the Shaper</a></span><span title="2024-01-04 02:44:29" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/9143243">1 year ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>✊</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div></div><div id="post-8870134" data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:8870134,&quot;user_id&quot;:1744130}" class="community_post has_vote_column has_replies"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a href="https://itch.io/profile/tuckertcs" class="avatar_container"><div style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/tuckertcs">Tuckertcs</a></span><span title="2023-11-11 17:38:21" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/8870134">1 year ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>What&#x27;s the difference between the 4 seasons in this pack and the actual 4 seasonal forest packs? The rockwork looks like they&#x27;re different. Do the others have more content than this one or are they essentially interchangeable?<br></p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies top_level_replies"><div id="post-8870203" data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:8870203,&quot;user_id&quot;:1278838}" class="community_post has_vote_column is_reply"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a href="https://itch.io/profile/seliel-the-shaper" class="avatar_container"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzIwMjE2NzM2LnBuZw==/25x25%23/%2BOhmGY.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/seliel-the-shaper">Seliel the Shaper</a></span><span title="2023-11-11 17:58:24" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/8870203">1 year ago</a></span> <span class="edit_message">(3 edits)</span> <span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>They are completely different, as you can see by looking at the grass, dirt, cliffs, trees, and water. The $10 version of this pack just borrows the color palettes from those sets. The 4 seasonal packs have maybe 5-6 times more content, as should be clear in the product descriptions.</p>
<p>However, it&#x27;s worth noting that the free sample version of the 4 seasonal packs are similar in size to this pack.</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div></div><div id="post-8739377" data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:8739377,&quot;user_id&quot;:8979761}" class="community_post has_vote_column has_replies"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a href="https://itch.io/profile/rut1122" class="avatar_container"><div style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog-cyan.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/rut1122">rut1122</a></span><span title="2023-10-16 14:24:22" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/8739377">1 year ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"><span class="upvotes">(+2)</span></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>This is a great pack! I used the free version to make a level in a short&nbsp;game built in Godot, and greatly enjoyed it. Thank you!<br><a href="https://rut1122.itch.io/game1">https://rut1122.itch.io/game1</a></p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies top_level_replies"><div id="post-8739847" data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:8739847,&quot;user_id&quot;:1278838}" class="community_post has_vote_column is_reply"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a href="https://itch.io/profile/seliel-the-shaper" class="avatar_container"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzIwMjE2NzM2LnBuZw==/25x25%23/%2BOhmGY.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/seliel-the-shaper">Seliel the Shaper</a></span><span title="2023-10-16 16:05:34" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/8739847">1 year ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>Looks cool, nice work! 😁👍</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle