title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a href="https://itch.io/profile/atta-2d-games" class="avatar_container"><div style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog-red.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/atta-2d-games">Atta 2D Games</a></span><span title="2021-05-29 21:48:28" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/3475400">4 years ago</a></span> <span class="edit_message">(3 edits)</span> <span class="vote_counts"><span class="upvotes">(+1)</span></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p><img src="https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzYwNzc3OTMucG5n/original/N%2FJP6q.png" loading="lazy">Hey, I&#x27;m new to all this and after hours of trying AND searching, I cannot figure out the bitmask for this (using Godot). can some one please help?</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies top_level_replies"><div id="post-3477204" data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:3477204,&quot;user_id&quot;:1278838}" class="community_post has_vote_column is_reply"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a href="https://itch.io/profile/seliel-the-shaper" class="avatar_container"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzIwMjE2NzM2LnBuZw==/25x25%23/%2BOhmGY.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/seliel-the-shaper">Seliel the Shaper</a></span><span title="2021-05-30 02:47:05" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/3477204">4 years ago</a></span> <span class="edit_message">(1 edit)</span> <span class="vote_counts"><span class="upvotes">(+1)</span></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>I don&#x27;t know Godot from a hole in the ground, but if you join my Discord server, we have a Godot help channel with other devs who might be and to answer your questions.</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div></div><div id="post-2477493" data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:2477493,&quot;user_id&quot;:3867184}" class="community_post has_vote_column has_replies"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a href="https://itch.io/profile/astrosurf" class="avatar_container"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzUwNTY4MjEucG5n/25x25%23/NN4Txp.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/astrosurf">Astrosurf</a></span><span title="2021-01-26 19:29:39" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/2477493">4 years ago</a></span> <span class="edit_message">(2 edits)</span> <span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>Hi, I&#x27;m new to this site.</p><p>I&nbsp;found, and experimented with this set all day yesterday&nbsp;and I am so blown away by how perfectly you style matched. This is my Favorite aesthetic. The games you cited as inspirations are all my favorite games from that generation.&nbsp;I also bought the village Bundle.</p>
<p>&nbsp;What do I need to do/pay in order to use these tiles to make Graphics/banners with words on them&nbsp;for like a personalized twitch&nbsp;page?&nbsp;I was originally planning to make my own tilesets and use these as a checklist for all the parts I might need to make,&nbsp;but I wanted to ask if I can make some stuff with your sets&nbsp;to use sooner, and then later replace.</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies top_level_replies"><div id="post-2477872" data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:2477872,&quot;user_id&quot;:1278838}" class="community_post has_vote_column is_reply has_replies"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a href="https://itch.io/profile/seliel-the-shaper" class="avatar_container"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzIwMjE2NzM2LnBuZw==/25x25%23/%2BOhmGY.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/seliel-the-shaper">Seliel the Shaper</a></span><span title="2021-01-26 20:42:34" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/2477872">4 years ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>Yeah, you can use my stuff to decorate your twitch page, that&#x27;s fine. Glad you like it 😊👍</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies"><div id="post-2478054" data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:2478054,&quot;user_id&quot;:3867184}" class="community_post has_vote_column is_reply"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a href="https://itch.io/profile/astrosurf" class="avatar_container"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzUwNTY4MjEucG5n/25x25%23/NN4Txp.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/astrosurf">Astrosurf</a></span><span title="2021-01-26 21:14:10" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/2478054">4 years ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>Awesome! Thank you so much!</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id="post-1981088" data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:1981088,&quot;user_id&quot;:1076877}" class="community_post has_vote_column"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a href="https://itch.io/profile/futureforge" class="avatar_container"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1hZ2UyL3VzZXIvMTA3Njg3Ny8xMzQ5NjAxLnBuZw==/25x25%23/Wg3rNR.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/futureforge">futureforge</a></span><span title="2020-09-09 20:27:44" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/1981088">4 years ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>This is beautiful</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div id="post-1624071" data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:1624071,&quot;user_id&quot;:1649373}" class="community_post has_vote_column has_replies"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a href="https://itch.io/profile/tarjan" class="avatar_container"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzM1ODEwOTEuanBn/25x25%23/1zlS15.jpg)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/tarjan">Tarjan</a></span><span title="2020-07-12 04:15:34" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/1624071">4 years ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>Your Mana Seed series fits my need so well, I will buy all of it over time. Great Pixel Art! Keep up the good work!<br></p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies top_level_replies"><div id="post-1624089" data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:1624089,&quot;user_id&quot;:1278838}" class="community_post has_vote_column is_reply"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a href="https://itch.io/profile/seliel-the-shaper" class="avatar_container"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzIwMjE2NzM2LnBuZw==/25x25%23/%2BOhmGY.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/seliel-the-shaper">Seliel the Shaper</a></span><span title="2020-07-12 04:27:53" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/1624089">4 years ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"><span class="upvotes">(+1)</span></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>Thank you very much, I&#x27;m glad you like it! 😁</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div></div><div id="post-1612518" data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:1612518,&quot;user_id&quot;:1899914}" class="community_post has_vote_column has_replies"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a href="https://itch.io/profile/tutterzoid" class="avatar_container"><div style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog-blue.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/tutterzoid">tutterzoid</a></span><span title="2020-07-07 23:56:26" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/1612518">4 years ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>Many will ask this .. What&#x27;s the license? CC0 or what? Can I use these assets in a commercial game and do I need to give credit? :)</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies top_level_replies"><div id="post-1612526" data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:1612526,&quot;user_id&quot;:1899914}" class="community_post has_vote_column is_reply has_replies"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a href="https://itch.io/profile/tutterzoid" class="avatar_container"><div style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog-blue.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/tutterzoid">tutterzoid</a></span><span title="2020-07-07 23:57:39" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/1612526">4 years ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p><a href="https://www.patreon.com/posts/mana-seed-user-27439171" referrerpolicy="origin" rel="nofollow noopener">https://www.patreon.com/posts/mana-seed-user-27439171</a></p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies"><div id="post-1612545" data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:1612545,&quot;user_id&quot;:1278838}" class="community_post has_vote_column is_reply has_replies"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a href="https://itch.io/profile/seliel-the-shaper" class="avatar_container"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzIwMjE2NzM2LnBuZw==/25x25%23/%2BOhmGY.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/seliel-the-shaper">Seliel the Shaper</a></span><span title="2020-07-08 00:01:42" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/1612545">4 years ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>Yes, you can use in a commercial product (the &quot;product&quot; referenced in the link). You do not have to credit me, but it would be nice.</p><p>I will try to make the wording a little more clear in the future 👍</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies"><div id="post-1740529" data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:1740529,&quot;user_id&quot;:1899914}" class="community_post has_vote_column is_reply"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a href="https://itch.io/profile/tutterzoid" class="avatar_container"><div style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog-blue.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/tutterzoid">tutterzoid</a></span><span title="2020-07-20 19:56:02" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/1740529">4 years ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>Thanks Seliel for making these assets available for use in a commercial product :)</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id="post-1549890" data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:1549890,&quot;user_id&quot;:900001}" class="community_post has_vote_column"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a href="https://itch.io/profile/poshalligator" class="avatar_container"><div style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog-cyan.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/poshalligator">PoshAlligator</a></span><span title="2020-06-17 12:00:29" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/1549890">5 years ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>Beautiful assets!</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div id="post-1538130" data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:1538130,&quot;user_id&quot;:2721550}" class="community_post has_vote_column"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a href="https://itch.io/profile/zsazsaz1" class="avatar_container"><div style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/zsazsaz1">zsazsaz1</a></span><span title="2020-06-14 22:20:53" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/1538130">5 years ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>Saw it on the justice bundle, and it really caught my eye.<br>It&#x27;s really beautifull</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div id="post-1523186" data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:1523186,&quot;user_id&quot;:2748688}" class="community_post has_vote_column has_replies"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a href="https://itch.io/profile/alex1203" class="avatar_container"><div style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog-gold.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/alex1203">Alex1203</a></span><span title="2020-06-11 10:20:06" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/1523186">5 years ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>Hi I don&#x27;t understand, is this a game? or is it just a pack with a bundle of skins to create your own game. If so, which plateform do we have to own to use this skin bundle?</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies top_level_replies"><div id="post-1523277" data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:1523277,&quot;user_id&quot;:1278838}" class="community_post has_vote_column is_reply"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a href="https://itch.io/profile/seliel-the-shaper" class="avatar_container"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzIwMjE2NzM2LnBuZw==/25x25%23/%2BOhmGY.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/seliel-the-shaper">Seliel the Shaper</a></span><span title="2020-06-11 11:06:57" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/1523277">5 years ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"><span class="upvotes">(+1)</span></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>This is a tileset for you to use in creating your own game. It&#x27;s not designed for any specific platform or engine.</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div></div><div id="post-938712" data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:938712,&quot;user_id&quot;:1119638}" class="community_post has_vote_column has_replies"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a href="https://itch.io/profile/dungeonmind" class="avatar_container"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzIxMDc2MjAzLmpwZw==/25x25%23/jd96I8.jpg)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/dungeonmind">Dungeonmind</a></span><span title="2019-09-01 23:26:54" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/938712">5 years ago</a></span> <span class="edit_message">(1 edit)</span> <span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>Yeah I really like your work as well. I hope you do keep going with it. I couldn&#x27;t afford the base pack today or this one. SO I&#x27;ll have to wait until I can</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies top_level_replies"><div id="post-939556" data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:939556,&quot;user_id&quot;:1278838}" class="community_post has_vote_column is_reply"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a href="https://itch.io/profile/seliel-the-shaper" class="avatar_container"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzIwMjE2NzM2LnBuZw==/25x25%23/%2BOhmGY.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/seliel-the-shaper">Seliel the Shaper</a></span><span title="2019-09-02 05:08:40" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/939556">5 years ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>I am planning to keep adding more for a long loooong time. I hope you&#x27;ll stick around for it!</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div></div><div id="post-811987" data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:811987,&quot;user_id&quot;:1354645}" class="community_post has_vote_column has_replies"><div id="last-post" class="post_anchor"></div><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fseliel-the-shaper.itch.io%2Fgentle-forest&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg version="1.1" width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a href="https://itch.io/profile/lvgames" class="avatar_container"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzg5MzAyMDIucG5n/25x25%23/%2BsQ99F.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/lvgames">LVGames</a></span><span title="2019-07-07 03:58:12" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/811987">5 years ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="pos